      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLAINE KEEPING (5) goes very well this course and distance starting 33 times for 19 wins and eight minors. Missed the frame latest (18.42) when fourth over 318m at this track in a NG. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. KIANDO DIVA (8) was below latest but prior to that a Grade 4/5 winner in quick time (18.28) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Has the ability and can find best this time. FUSION ROSE (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 18.40 beating Hard Style Chick. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and three minor placings from four starts. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. HOPE'S TREASURE (7) was in the money last time at this track (18.31) in a NG, finishing a 3 length third. Has already won two times from this draw.",
